---
title: One-Pot Italian Noodle Soup with Chicken Sausage, Penne & Parmesan Toasts
description: This is chicken noodle soup the way your Italian grandma would’ve made it. Naturally, there’s a soul-soothing broth flavored with garlic and Italian herbs. And it’s got all the veggies to make you strong, like carrot, tomato, and spinach. Although that old-world charm really shines through in the penne pasta, chicken sausage, and sprinkle of Parmesan cheese, not to mention a side of cheesy toast for dunking. If you want to claim this one as a generations-old family recipe, we’ll keep it a secret.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-noodle-soup-29f3f264.jpg
